{"tid":1005121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳通用汽車擬下周一裁減4000北美員工","createTime":"2019-02-02T04:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T04:07:03.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"af506e2f932eed78766b401c99cfa2c972c5f05a","tid":1005121,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:08:05.000Z","msg":"傳通用汽車擬下周一裁減4000北美員工<br />\n2/2/2019 4:23<br />\n<br />\n        通用汽車據報計劃下星期一裁減約4000名北美員工.<br />\n<br />\n        CNBC引述兩名消息人士報道, 通用汽車高層希望在下星期三, 公布第四季業績之前, 盡可能完成更多裁員目標. 通用汽車發言人回應說, 公司並無確定的裁員時間表, 強調會先和員工溝通, 而員工的意願會是優先考慮.<br />\n        通用汽車去年11月宣布, 進行大規模重組, 計劃關閉北美5間廠房, 並裁減一成五僱員, 相當於1萬4700個職位, 以節省60億美元. 美加兩國總統都對裁員計劃表達不滿. 不過, 公司其後向1萬7700個員工提出自願離職計劃, 並將部分調往其他工廠工作, 強制裁員的情況未如外界想像般嚴重."},{"pid":"2e7a1159a2fb2acc50c0ee9a9ba0eda1b8df3587","tid":1005121,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Cx7uO0sXAAARHN0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCx7uO0sXAAARHN0.jpg&h=88de4777&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fac0f059b61bb16899ed622256675236837452b3","tid":1005121,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e7a1159a2fb2acc50c0ee9a9ba0eda1b8df3587","tid":1005121,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Cx7uO0sXAAARHN0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCx7uO0sXAAARHN0.jpg&h=88de4777&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:11:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed75dfa4ef4180d0b55cab3b0b215cb8923cd9de","tid":1005121,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fac0f059b61bb16899ed622256675236837452b3","tid":1005121,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e7a1159a2fb2acc50c0ee9a9ba0eda1b8df3587","tid"